# Git Configuration Recommendations
# =====================================
# Run these commands on all developer machines to ensure consistent behavior

# 1. Ensure Git handles case sensitivity consistently
git config core.ignorecase false  # Detect case changes on all platforms

# 2. Normalize line endings (prevents issues across Windows/Mac/Linux)
git config core.autocrlf input     # Use LF line endings consistently

# 3. Use standard file renaming detection
git config rename.rewrite true
